snippet.title: Tactical Vengeance: Play The Games - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
OFFICIAL TRAILER. Tactical Vengeance: Play The Games. 

Our first project, a Early Access on Steam, as we are proud on! - Join us today and follow our steps into a game world! 

AVAILABLE ON STEAM! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2252870/Tactical_Vengeance_Play_The_Game/?beta=0

This game is a Firstperson Multiplayer Shootergame. Play 6 Different Match, on different Maps. Fight for your team to be the best team and become Player of the Match. Own Medals by shooting your enemies! Get higher Level and get Rank Medals as well. 


We hope you will like the game!  Stay well, and Play The Games.
